":2330481,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:36:01.000Z","msg":"搞撚到博士問答咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d87f0b388a615586835e4057e510c94a4ae7a5","tid":2330481,"uid":268429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:43:52.000Z","msg":"條線要幾長?"},{"pid":"44a1f7912312898c65d0a86032e62cef98cf9b8f","tid":2330481,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"無俾錢問<br />\n打多幾隻字算俾面你啦"},{"pid":"b07494a6906a996c2742c95968bfebca715204d4","tid":2330481,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e408a99cca1fa31340cff8030c5ad2aa893d47c","tid":2330481,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbc9a0de750db72cc56bc63883fbe85fef762b69","tid":2330481,"uid":363330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:32:47.000Z","msg":"代答<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該採取 先增值後現金流 嘅策略<br />\n如果間公司本身係有質素 眼前嘅股價波動係唔需要理會<br />\n你選嘅股亦都有一定質素 不過早前股價有啲被高估 而家調整緊返去合理價 再加上疫症影響 短期內股價未必有大增幅<br />\n等疫情轉好後 資金有望重新進入股票市場<br />\n另外 建議你分散風險 例如分注買入2800投資一籃子有質素嘅公司<br />\n可以觀望穩定增長<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都識答<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:35:06.000Z","msg":"可以整個bot自動回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:57:35.000Z","msg":"代埋台灣財經節目答<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n疫情嘅關係 啲資金暫時會傾向流入債市或者黃金去避險<br />\n近日憧憬疫苗開發完成 短期內或者有小幅度嘅向上都唔定<br />\n但一切都要等疫苗嘅效果明朗咗先回復正常<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅疫情令到WFH開始成為常態<br />\n即係少咗通勤因素 啲人喺置業嘅時候<br />\n或者會開始考慮啲稍為遠少少但平啲嘅地方<br />\n咁有可能令到啲二線地方嘅樓價同租金增長 但反過來 啲中心區域嘅租金可能會下降都唔定<br />\n不過令到其他地區活化喺上嚟 長遠嚟講係對整體經濟發展有利<br />\n但諗住喺啲中心地區買物業嘅話就要諗諗先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知咁得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6dae5e9f04c26a7febaba374e57bb60b60fc51","tid":2330481,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46210ce12b1258f6014df8463bad0ee62e68ba5f","tid":2330481,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:36:01.000Z","msg":"搞撚到博士問答咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T08:42:50.000Z","msg":"屌, 以前曹宏威個網站好撚正,咩人問問題佢都答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知有冇人記得."}]}